- Extend `DrushCommands` (not `AnnotatedCommands` base).
- Use `#[CLI\Command]`, `#[CLI\Option]`, `#[CLI\Argument]` — **no docblocks**.
- Return `int` (`self::SUCCESS` or `self::FAILURE`).
- Use `$this->io()->success()` for user-facing success messages.
- Use `$this->io()->table()` for tabular output.
- Use `$this->logger()` for internal debug/verbose logging.

