In Drush 12, use **PHP 8 constructor property promotion with type hints** — autowiring is enabled by default for services.

✅ Correct (Drush 12+):
```php
<?php

namespace Drupal\my_module\Drush\Commands;

use Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityTypeManagerInterface;
use Drupal\my_module\Service\ReportGeneratorInterface;
use Drush\Commands\DrushCommands;

final class MyModuleCommands extends DrushCommands {

  public function __construct(
    private EntityTypeManagerInterface $entityTypeManager,
    private ReportGeneratorInterface $reportGenerator
  ) {
    parent::__construct();
